 of Kentucky|Kentucky]]\n | notes = \n | maderoster     = yes\n | hof = \n}}\n{{NFL team draft entry\n | round = 9\n | pick         = 249\n | player         = [[John Teltschik]]\n | position      = [[Punter (American football)|Punter]]\n | college   = [[University of Texas at Austin|Texas]]\n | notes = \n | maderoster     = no\n | hof = \n}}\n{{NFL team draft entry\n | round = 10\n | pick         = 277\n | player         = Barton Hundley\n | position      = [[Defensive back]]\n | college   = Kansas State\n | notes = \n | maderoster     = no\n | hof = \n}}\n{{NFL team draft entry\n | round = 11\n | pick         = 305\n | player         = [[Glen Kozlowski]]\n | position      = [[Wide receiver]]\n | college   = [[Brigham Young University|Brigham Young]]\n | notes = \n | maderoster     = yes\n | hof = \n}}\n{{NFL team draft end}}\n\n==Staff==\n{| class=\"toccolours\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse;\"\n|-\n| colspan=\"7\" style=\"text-align:center;\"|'''Coaching Staff of 1986 season'''\n|-\n|valign=\"top\"| \n'''Front office'''\n* [[Virginia Halas McCaskey]] \u2013 ''Owner''\n* [[Michael McCaskey]] \u2013 ''Team president''\n* [[Jerry Vainisi]] \u2013 ''General manager''\n* [[Ray Earley]] \u2013 ''Equipment manager''\n* [[Gary Haeger]] \u2013 ''Assistant equipment manager''\n* [[Rod Graves]] \u2013 ''Director of player personnel''\n'''Coaches'''\n* [[Mike Ditka]] \u2013 ''Head coach''\n* [[Steve Kazor]] \u2013 ''Assistant head coach''{{ref label|Other|a|a1}}\n* [[Ed Hughes]] \u2013 ''Offensive coordinator''\n* [[Vince Tobin]] \u2013 ''Defensive coordinator''\n|width=\"25\"|&nbsp;\n|valign=\"top\"|\n'''Position coaches'''\n* [[Greg Landry]] \u2013 ''Quarterbacks''\n* [[Johnny Roland]] \u2013 ''Running backs''\n* [[Dick Stanfel]] \u2013 ''Offensive line''\n* [[John Levra]] \u2013 ''Defensive line''\n* [[Dave McGinnis]] \u2013 ''Linebackers''\n* [[Jim LaRue]] \u2013 ''Secondary''\n'''Trainers'''\n* [[Brian McCaskey]] \u2013 ''Assistant trainer''\n* [[Clyde Emrich]] \u201