gie Phillips]]\n\n'''Defensive backs'''\n*23 [[Shaun Gayle]]\n*25 [[Todd Bell]]\n*36 ''[[Maurice Douglass]]''\n\n'''Safeties'''\n*22 [[Dave Duerson]] SS\n*45 [[Gary Fencik]] FS\n|width=\"25\"|&nbsp;\n|valign=\"top\"|\n\n'''Reserve Lists'''\n{{NFLplayer|21|Leslie Frazier|CB|IR}}\n{{NFLplayer|49|''Riley Walton''|TE|IR}}\n{{NFLplayer|85|Dennis McKinnon|WR|IR}}\n{{NFLplayer|93|Glen Kozlowski|WR|IR}}\n\n<small>''Rookies in italics''<br /></small>\n|}\n\n====Depth chart====\n{{CFB Team Depth Chart\n| OScheme         = Pro-Set\n| DScheme         = 4-3\n| SpecialTeams    = Yes\n| KeyReserves     = No\n| 3Deep           = No\n| QB_Starter      = [[Jim McMahon]]\n| QB_Backup       = [[Mike Tomczak]]\n| QB_Third        = \n| RB1_Starter     = [[Walter Payton]]\n| RB1_Backup      = \n| RB1_Third       = \n| RB2_Starter     = \n| RB2_Backup      = \n| RB2_Third       = \n| FB_Starter      = [[Matt Suhey]]\n| FB_Backup       = \n| FB_Third        = \n| SB1_Starter     = \n| SB1_Backup      = \n| SB1_Third       = \n| SB2_Starter     = \n| SB2_Backup      = \n| SB2_Third       = \n| WR1_Starter     = [[Willie Gault]]\n| WR1_Backup      = \n| WR1_Third       = \n| WR1_SchoolName  = \n| WR2_Starter     = [[Keith Ortego]]\n| WR2_Backup      = \n| WR2_Third       = \n| WR2_SchoolName  = \n| WR3_Starter     = \n| WR3_Backup      = \n| WR3_Third       = \n| WR3_SchoolName  = \n| WR4_Starter     = \n| WR4_Backup      = \n| WR4_Third       = \n| WR4_SchoolName  = \n| TE1_Starter     = [[Emery Moorehead]]\n| TE1_Backup      = \n| TE1_Third       = \n| TE2_Starter     = \n| TE2_Backup      = \n| TE2_Third       = \n| LT_Starter      = [[Jimbo Covert]]\n| LT_Backup       = \n| LT_Third        = \n| LG_Starter      = [[Mark Bortz]]\n| LG_Backup       = \n| LG_Third        = \n| C_Starter       = [[Jay Hilgenberg]]\n| C_Backup        = \n| C_Third         = \n| RG_Starter      = [[Tom Thayer]]\n| RG_Backup       = \n| RG_Third        = \n| RT_Starter      = [[Keith Van Horne]]\n| RT_Backup    